instruction: Create an epic adventure for a group of teenagers.
output: The group of teenagers join forces to explore an ancient temple in the heart of the jungle. After fighting their way past wild beasts and battling a pack of fierce warriors, they discover a hidden chamber containing the legendary Sword of Destiny. The teens must then race against the clock to deliver the sword to its rightful owner, a powerful wizard who will reward them with unimaginable riches. Along the way, they must brave treacherous conditions, outsmart sly adversaries and use their wits to solve ancient puzzles.
